# CLAUDE.md — project instructions (starter)

## Project
One paragraph: what this repo is, the stack, the one architectural fact that prevents the most wrong assumptions.

## Commands
- build: `<cmd>`
- test: `<cmd>`   (run before claiming anything works)
- run: `<cmd>`

## Conventions
- Code style: <formatter/linter and how to run it>
- Tests live in <path>, named <pattern>; mirror an existing test file's style.
- Commits: conventional commits.

## Boundaries
- Never touch: <paths — generated code, vendored dirs, prod config>.
