## Gotchas
One line each, grown over time — add a line whenever the agent makes the same mistake twice.

## Scaling note
Larger repos: keep this file global-only and add per-directory CLAUDE.md files (src/, tests/, infra/) for directory-specific conventions — Claude Code loads them when working in each directory. Never duplicate a rule at two levels; globals stay here, locals stay local.
